# TinaCMS generated client (regenerated by the build) and the compiled admin
# app bundle. tina-lock.json and public/uploads/ are NOT here on purpose:
# tina-lock.json is read by Tina Cloud to index content without a build, and
# uploads/ is repo-based media, real content that belongs in git with the docs.
**/tina/__generated__/
docs/public/admin/
